<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>Come on, Finn, don’t be so mysterious. Everybody was looking at her. She looked like a supermodel! Is it serious? No offence, but how did you manage to attract a woman like that?</p> 
<p><strong>Finn</strong><br />What do you mean? I’m very handsome! But she’s not my girlfriend…</p> 
