<p><strong>Neil<br /></strong>I've lost count. Let me see, I left school at 18, did an apprenticeship for 2 years and then I joined the BBC in 1995.</p> 
<p><strong>Helen<br /></strong>That's twenty years. My goodness! So you are part of the furniture at the BBC!</p> 
