<p><strong>Helen<br /> </strong>Hello and welcome to The English We Speak. I'm Helen.<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p> 
<p><strong>Rob</strong><strong><br /> </strong>And I'm Rob. Hello! Err, Helen are you feeling OK? You're looking a bit tired.</p> 
