<p><strong>Neil<br /></strong>Ooh – <strong>to spill the beans</strong> – meaning to reveal your secrets. It's often used when you share a secret you didn't mean to share!</p> 
<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>Another great phrase. So, what do you fancy for lunch?&nbsp;</p> 
<p><strong>Neil<br /></strong>Well, it has to be a full English breakfast. With beans and… sausages!</p> 
<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>But of course! Bye everyone!&nbsp;</p> 
