<p><strong>Neil<br /></strong>It was a knee-jerk reaction. And in English we can say that someone has a knee-jerk reaction when they act after an event without thinking carefully.</p> 
<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>Let's hear some examples of 'knee-jerk reaction'.</p> 
<p><strong>Examples<br /></strong>After the terrorist attack, the government should be careful to avoid a knee-jerk reaction. A declaration of war could lead to even bigger problems later.</p> 
