<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>(embarrassed) Right. OK. Let's hear some examples while I wrap myself in a towel:</p> 
<p><strong>Examples<br /></strong>The deadline's tomorrow and we haven't even started! The heat's really on now.</p> 
