<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>So a <strong>fuddy-duddy</strong> is someone who is old-fashioned and sometimes pompous. But Rob, being a <strong>fuddy-duddy</strong> isn't all bad.</p> 
<p><strong>Rob<br /></strong>Oh yes? Boring, old-fashioned – how can that be a good thing?</p> 
<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>Well, you make us all laugh.</p> 
