<p><strong>Finn<br /></strong>The pink one?</p>
<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>No, they are very similar. It’s six of one, half a dozen of the other…</p>
<p><strong>Finn<br /></strong>Oh, you’re not helping! I’m off, bye.</p>
<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>Wait…</p>"
