<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>Hangry? Don't you mean 'angry'?</p> 
<p><strong>Sian<br /></strong>No, 'hangry'. 'Hangry' describes someone who is angry – or irritable – as a result of being hungry. Like me today – I'm feeling a bit annoyed because I haven't eaten breakfast!</p> 
<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>You certainly are! So 'hangry' is a combination of 'angry' and 'hungry'?</p> 
