<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>Interesting. You wouldn't catch me getting 'hangry' though, I'm always very chilled.</p> 
<p><strong>Sian<br /></strong>Is that right Feifei? You know, I'm feeling much happier after eating that chocolate bar. Shall we do the programme again? I feel ready now.&nbsp;</p> 
<p><strong>Feifei<br /></strong>No! come on that will do. I'm starving!</p> 
