<p><strong>Examples</strong></p> 
<p>The interviewer raised tough questions but Ma Yun was on the ball.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>Financial management is not a job that everyone can do. You have to keep your eye on the ball at all times.<strong><em>&nbsp;</em></strong></p> 
<p><strong>Li<br /></strong>And if you want to learn English well you can stay on the ball with <a href=""http://www.bbclearningenglish.com/"">bbclearningenglish.com</a>.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p> 
